### Familias
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/families
Accept: application/json

### Familias por standard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/families?standard=AISC
Accept: application/json

### Perfiles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### Perfiles AISC
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles?standard=AISC&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Perfiles Euro
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/profiles?standard=EURO&page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Items del catálogo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/catalog/items?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json
